C effect at the\ntetragonal-orthorhombic transition for electric fields applied along the [001]\npseudo-cubic direction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2017 09:07:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-12"}
