an be used for the design of computing\nelements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2017 14:59:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Nov 2017 12:10:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-29"}
